	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nah, it won't do you any good if there's extra protection checking for the video frequency. All it would do is allow the cart to boot on your NTSC Snes but as soon as the game code will check the video frequency it will give you a ''Not designed for your region'' type of screen.

		

