	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can use Ucon64 to remove common copy protections. After you did that, it does not matter which CIC is installed on the board. You still need the correct CIC key for the CIC lock in the SNES though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


